### Naming Conventions

| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|------------|---------|
| Files (components) | kebab-case | `app-layout.tsx`, `tenant-select.tsx` |
| Files (utilities) | kebab-case | `api-client.ts` |
| Files (hooks) | kebab-case with use- | `use-product-stats.ts` |
| Components | PascalCase | `AppLayout`, `TenantSelect` |
| Hooks | camelCase with use | `useProductStats` |
| Types/Interfaces | PascalCase | `Product`, `User`, `Tenant` |
| Constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `API_URL` |
| Functions | camelCase | `formatPrice` |

### Code Style (Biome)

- **Indentation**: Tabs (not spaces)
- **Line Width**: 100 characters
- **Quotes**: Double quotes for strings
- **Semicolons**: Always use semicolons
- **Trailing Commas**: ES5 style (objects, arrays)
- **Path Aliases**: Use `@/` for `src/` imports

