## Multitenancy (Custom Implementation - 100% Refine Official Pattern)

This project uses a **custom multitenancy implementation** that follows the exact same pattern as `@refinedev/enterprise` + `@refinedev/multitenancy` packages (which are paid/enterprise features). Our implementation is free and provides full control.

### Architecture Overview

| Component | Location | Purpose |
|-----------|----------|---------|
| `MultitenancyProvider` | `src/providers/multitenancy.tsx` | React context for tenant state management |
| `useMultitenancy` | `src/providers/multitenancy.tsx` | Hook to access tenant context anywhere |
| `useRouterAdapter` | `src/providers/multitenancy.tsx` | Extracts tenantId from URL params |
| `useLocalStorageAdapter` | `src/providers/multitenancy.tsx` | Alternative: persists tenant in localStorage |
| `WithTenant` | `src/providers/multitenancy.tsx` | Wrapper component with loading/fallback states |
| `tenantAwareDataProvider` | `src/providers/data-provider.ts` | Auto-filters all CRUD by tenantId |

### Tenant Interface

```typescript
interface Tenant {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  logo?: string;
  [key: string]: unknown;  // Extensible
}
```

### Setup Pattern (Same as Refine Official Docs)

```typescript
// 1. fetchTenants function - returns { tenants, defaultTenant }
const fetchTenants = async () => ({
  tenants: SAMPLE_TENANTS,
  defaultTenant: SAMPLE_TENANTS[0],
});

// 2. Use adapter inside Router context
function AppWithMultitenancy() {
  const adapter = useRouterAdapter();  // or useLocalStorageAdapter()

  return (
    <MultitenancyProvider adapter={adapter} fetchTenants={fetchTenants}>
      <WithTenant
        fallback={<Navigate to={`/${DEFAULT_TENANT}`} />}
        loadingComponent={<Loading />}
      >
        {/* Routes with /:tenantId prefix */}
      </WithTenant>
    </MultitenancyProvider>
  );
}
```

### Route Structure

All routes follow `/:tenantId/*` pattern:
```typescript
resources={[
  { name: "dashboard", list: "/:tenantId" },
  { name: "events", list: "/:tenantId/events", show: "/:tenantId/events/:id" },
  { name: "orders", list: "/:tenantId/orders", show: "/:tenantId/orders/:id" },
]}
```

### Tenant-Aware Data Provider

The `tenantAwareDataProvider` automatically handles multitenancy for all CRUD operations:

| Method | Behavior |
|--------|----------|
| `getList` | Auto-adds `tenantId` filter to all queries |
| `getOne` | Validates record belongs to current tenant |
| `getMany` | Filters results to only tenant-owned records |
| `create` | Auto-injects `tenantId` into new records |
| `update` | Validates tenant ownership before update |
| `deleteOne` | Validates tenant ownership before delete |

**tenantId is passed via `meta` object:**
```typescript
// Refine automatically passes meta.tenantId to all data provider methods
const result = await dataProvider.getList({
  resource: "products",
  meta: { tenantId: "brand-1" }  // Auto-injected by Refine
});
```

### Using useMultitenancy Hook

```typescript
const {
  tenant,       // Current tenant object
  tenants,      // All available tenants
  isLoading,    // Loading state
  setTenant,    // Switch tenant (updates URL)
  deleteTenant, // Clear tenant
  fetchTenants  // Re-fetch tenant list
} = useMultitenancy();

// Example: Display current tenant
<span>{tenant?.name}</span>

// Example: Switch tenant
<button onClick={() => setTenant(tenants[1])}>
  Switch to {tenants[1].name}
</button>
```

### Tenant Select Component

```typescript
import { TenantSelect } from "@/components/tenant-select";

// In sidebar/header
<TenantSelect />
```

### Key Features

1. **URL-Based Routing**: Tenant ID in URL enables bookmarking and sharing
2. **Automatic Data Isolation**: All API requests filtered by tenant
3. **Access Validation**: Prevents cross-tenant data access
4. **Seamless Switching**: Change tenant = URL update = data refresh
5. **Loading States**: Built-in loading and fallback handling

### Comparison with Official Refine Enterprise

| Feature | Refine Enterprise | Our Implementation |
|---------|-------------------|-------------------|
| Pattern | ✅ Same | ✅ Same |
| API Interface | ✅ Same | ✅ Same |
| URL Adapter | ✅ useRouterAdapter | ✅ useRouterAdapter |
| LocalStorage Adapter | ✅ | ✅ |
| WithTenant | ✅ | ✅ |
| fetchTenants format | `{ tenants, defaultTenant }` | `{ tenants, defaultTenant }` |
| meta.tenantId | ✅ | ✅ |
| **License** | Paid Enterprise | **Free** |
| **Dependency** | @refinedev/enterprise | **None** |

